<ab> <title>XI.  HVMNVS IN TEMPORE TRISTITIAE. </title> </ab>
          <l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Deus perenne gaudium,  </l>
            <l n="2">Pax Christe cordis anxii  </l>
            <l n="3">Portusque fluctuantium,  </l>
            <l n="4">Quem nec procella, turbidis  </l>
            <l n="5">6 Si uerrat ima motibus,  </l>
            <l n="6">Potest fugare a pectore.  </l> 

          <l n="7"><milestone unit="para"/>Qui mersa ponto <sic>subleuaa</sic>,  </l>
            <l n="8">Qui subiugata sarcinis,  </l>
            <l n="9">Qui dux prophetae naufragi,  </l>
             <l n="10">Dum uiuit esca beluae,   </l>
            <l n="11">Dum nescit aequor quod tenet,  </l>
            <l n="12">Tutum <choice><sic>fferiuo</sic><corr>ferino</corr></choice> e gutture  </l>
            <l n="13"><sic>Eiactor</sic> abrumpis cibum.  </l>
            <l n="14">Diro reductus remige,  </l>
             <l n="15">Custode saluus pessimo,   </l>
            <l n="16"><choice><sic>Yates</sic><corr>Vates</corr></choice> locutus te deum  </l>
            <l n="17">Tunc iussa gessit fortior.  </l> 

          <l n="18"><milestone unit="para"/>Inmunda lymphis sobrium  </l>
            <l n="19">Per busta tetris uexerat:  </l>
             <l n="20">Viuens <choice><sic>septilera</sic><corr>sepulcra</corr></choice> pertulit,   </l>
            <l n="21"><choice><sic>Yiuentis</sic><corr>Viuentis</corr></choice> urnae <choice><sic>prandtum</sic><corr>prandium</corr></choice>.  </l> 

          <l n="22"><milestone unit="para" rend="script"/>Secreta coeti prodidit  </l>


