          <l n="24"><milestone unit="para"/>Sic nos precamur, rex deus,  </l>
             <l n="25">Maerore fractos ut cibum   </l>
            <l n="26">De uentre curarum rape.  </l> 

          <l n="27"><milestone unit="para"/>Viuit <choice><sic>medtillis</sic><corr>medullis</corr></choice> quod necat,  </l>
            <l n="28">Turbantur alta <choice><sic>uisoerum</sic><corr>uiscerum</corr></choice>.  </l> 

          <l n="29"><milestone unit="para"/>In fonte <choice><sic>barnis</sic><corr>carnis</corr></choice> ardor est,  </l>
             <l n="30">Qui mergit urit adficit:   </l>
            <l n="31">Sed si serenus aspicis,-  </l>
            <l n="32">Pressura gignet gaudium.  </l> 

          

